WEBVTT

00:15.460 --> 00:19.960
♪During the dark night♪

00:20.100 --> 00:22.750
♪A guiding light♪

00:23.260 --> 00:25.050
♪Just like you♪

00:25.460 --> 00:29.750
♪Makes life turn bright♪

00:30.330 --> 00:35.180
♪Breaking free from darkness♪

00:35.400 --> 00:38.880
♪You gave me strength♪

00:39.230 --> 00:41.780
♪Running for truth♪

00:41.800 --> 00:45.850
♪I find my path♪

00:46.600 --> 00:50.580
♪Drawing on the hope♪

00:51.200 --> 00:54.580
♪That you render me♪

00:55.130 --> 00:58.010
♪In this long journey♪

00:58.260 --> 01:01.680
♪I run on lightly♪

01:19.180 --> 01:22.980
[Reborn]
[Adapted from Qiang Yu's work, Reborn]

01:23.820 --> 01:26.370
He's going to study abroad?

01:26.370 --> 01:27.570
Yes, he is.

01:27.980 --> 01:29.490
His parents reached an agreement

01:29.530 --> 01:31.170
on his future plans.

01:31.700 --> 01:33.060
He'll go to France to study

01:33.170 --> 01:35.060
and become a good doctor.

01:35.860 --> 01:37.700
He fails

01:37.700 --> 01:38.539
most of his papers

01:38.539 --> 01:40.050
because he doesn't care about them.

01:40.490 --> 01:41.810
But he focuses a lot

01:41.810 --> 01:43.490
on learning a foreign language.

01:44.490 --> 01:45.650
If all goes as planned,

01:47.050 --> 01:48.370
he'd settle abroad.

01:52.140 --> 01:53.100
He and we

01:55.009 --> 01:57.130
are worlds apart.

02:00.260 --> 02:01.050
You're both

02:01.650 --> 02:02.940
only 18 years old.

02:03.130 --> 02:03.980
I'm worried

02:04.980 --> 02:06.690
you might make a rash decision

02:07.010 --> 02:08.539
in the heat of the moment.

02:09.009 --> 02:10.620
Since you are going to Jiangzhou,

02:10.620 --> 02:12.050
where you'll know no one,

02:12.090 --> 02:13.410
and you haven't even finished school,

02:13.860 --> 02:15.010
this decision

02:15.010 --> 02:17.130
could completely rewrite your lives.

02:18.690 --> 02:20.770
I don't know about you,

02:23.620 --> 02:24.940
but Sheng's future won't be better

02:27.020 --> 02:29.290
than the one
his parents have planned for him.

02:33.380 --> 02:34.490
I'm heading back.

02:34.690 --> 02:35.740
When Ming Sheng comes back,

02:35.740 --> 02:37.130
don't tell him I was here.

02:37.210 --> 02:38.260
I don't want him to worry.

02:40.900 --> 02:42.540
Thank you for talking with me.

02:43.260 --> 02:44.050
I'm leaving.

02:53.650 --> 02:58.530
[Episode 13]
[The Moon Is Beautiful Tonight]

03:15.000 --> 03:19.630
[French: Guidance and Testing]

03:23.650 --> 03:27.930
[Huanzhou Departure Bus Routes]

03:40.820 --> 03:41.410
Thank you.

03:41.610 --> 03:42.500
You're welcome.

03:44.440 --> 03:45.450
Wait!

03:46.570 --> 03:47.780
I told you not to run off

03:47.780 --> 03:48.340
and wait for me.

03:48.610 --> 03:49.780
What would I do

03:50.010 --> 03:50.890
if you got lost

03:50.890 --> 03:52.290
and I couldn't find you?

03:53.170 --> 03:53.660
Come on.

04:20.450 --> 04:21.260
Qiao Qingyu?

04:22.820 --> 04:23.450
Qiao Qingyu!

04:24.450 --> 04:25.980
It's me. What's wrong?

04:29.660 --> 04:30.170
Nothing.

04:30.170 --> 04:32.340
I was just teasing you.

04:34.340 --> 04:35.060
Immature.

04:36.970 --> 04:40.400
♪Under the sunlight♪

04:41.290 --> 04:42.010
Qiao Qingyu.

04:42.780 --> 04:43.500
What?

04:44.850 --> 04:45.570
Don't go anywhere.

04:45.570 --> 04:47.409
♪Raise me up, hold me high♪

04:47.409 --> 04:48.260
I'll be back soon.

04:48.820 --> 04:49.610
Got it?

04:49.610 --> 04:52.150
♪Only you♪

04:52.720 --> 04:55.500
♪During the dark night♪

04:55.500 --> 04:55.980
Okay.

04:57.200 --> 05:00.100
♪A guiding light♪

05:00.100 --> 05:01.260
You know nothing

05:01.450 --> 05:02.850
about that girl from the Qiao family.

05:03.980 --> 05:05.220
She's always hanging out
with troublemakers.

05:05.220 --> 05:07.250
♪Makes life turn bright♪

05:07.340 --> 05:09.100
Why do you think their noodle house

05:09.500 --> 05:11.380
is always so rowdy?

05:11.730 --> 05:13.610
It's because she attracts
all the riff-raff.

05:13.980 --> 05:15.010
Otherwise,

05:15.170 --> 05:16.730
why would they even go there
to harass her?

05:17.340 --> 05:19.060
You can't judge a book by its cover.

05:19.600 --> 05:23.980
♪I find my path♪

05:23.980 --> 05:25.380
Honestly, I'm not at all surprised

05:25.500 --> 05:26.500
by what happened to her…

05:26.540 --> 05:27.060
Hey!

05:27.290 --> 05:28.500
What's wrong with him?

05:28.540 --> 05:29.340
That boy.

05:29.730 --> 05:31.260
Watch where you are going.

05:31.260 --> 05:32.890
A pack of cigarettes, ma'am.

05:33.450 --> 05:34.340
What kind of attitude is that?

05:34.340 --> 05:35.540
He should at least apologize!

05:35.820 --> 05:38.500
♪I run lightly♪

05:38.500 --> 05:40.370
I bought some food,

05:40.370 --> 05:42.409
and I also got you some clothes.

05:42.700 --> 05:43.730
These should be

05:43.730 --> 05:45.100
about your size.

05:45.409 --> 05:46.370
We'll grab

05:46.409 --> 05:47.930
the rest

05:47.930 --> 05:48.780
in Jiangzhou.

05:51.580 --> 05:52.370
Oh, right.

05:53.460 --> 05:54.659
I got you this.

05:55.340 --> 05:56.490
Heating pads.

05:56.730 --> 05:57.780
Stick them inside your clothes

05:57.780 --> 05:59.140
before you go out tomorrow.

05:59.490 --> 06:00.660
It's still pretty cold outside.

06:01.730 --> 06:02.930
I don't want
to have to take care of a sick person

06:03.290 --> 06:04.700
on the road.

06:05.780 --> 06:06.700
I'll leave them here.

06:15.780 --> 06:16.580
This is

06:16.700 --> 06:18.780
my red envelope money,
saved up since I was five.

06:19.140 --> 06:20.410
I've saved it for 12 years,

06:20.900 --> 06:22.140
and now I've got 17,000.

06:23.020 --> 06:25.220
You keep it.

06:26.290 --> 06:28.340
I may lose it.
You'd better keep it yourself.

06:28.540 --> 06:30.290
Just do as I say.

06:30.290 --> 06:31.020
Take it.

06:34.100 --> 06:35.580
This is all I have left.

06:36.020 --> 06:37.810
Keep it safe.

06:42.020 --> 06:43.170
And tomorrow,

06:43.700 --> 06:45.409
we can't take the train

06:45.409 --> 06:46.490
or a plane.

06:46.490 --> 06:47.610
So early in the morning,

06:48.020 --> 06:49.020
I'll get us a cab.

06:49.220 --> 06:51.050
If all goes well,
we'll reach Jiangzhou in the afternoon.

06:53.170 --> 06:54.540
Have you thought about

06:54.610 --> 06:56.220
what we'll eat, where we'll stay,

06:56.290 --> 06:58.610
how we'll make money,
and how you'll explain it to your dad

06:59.100 --> 07:00.540
once we get to Jiangzhou?

07:00.580 --> 07:01.540
I've thought about it.

07:01.810 --> 07:03.850
I have an online friend in Jiangzhou.

07:03.980 --> 07:05.460
He can help me

07:05.460 --> 07:07.610
get a night shift job at a supermarket.

07:07.850 --> 07:10.170
We can stay at the employee dormitory

07:10.170 --> 07:11.100
for the time being.

07:12.050 --> 07:13.700
We'll figure out the rest

07:14.290 --> 07:15.730
one step at a time.

07:18.050 --> 07:19.900
This isn't the life
you should be living.

07:21.170 --> 07:22.730
I decide what my life

07:23.290 --> 07:24.610
should be like.

07:25.100 --> 07:27.410
But my family situation
has nothing to do with you.

07:27.410 --> 07:29.220
You don't need
to turn your life upside down for me.

07:29.220 --> 07:30.930
I'm not leaving because of you.

07:32.140 --> 07:33.610
I've always wanted

07:33.980 --> 07:34.980
to run away from home

07:35.100 --> 07:36.490
and escape my dad's control.

07:37.900 --> 07:39.170
You and I just happened to end up

07:39.850 --> 07:40.810
traveling the same road.

07:41.850 --> 07:43.730
But what if this decision is wrong?

07:44.140 --> 07:45.730
When we're 28

07:45.730 --> 07:47.020
or 38

07:47.140 --> 07:48.980
and look back,

07:48.980 --> 07:50.930
we might think this was stupid and regret it.

07:52.659 --> 07:53.409
Qiao Qingyu.

07:54.850 --> 07:55.700
You're not backing out

07:55.700 --> 07:57.100
before we even leave, are you?

07:57.780 --> 07:59.140
You're not

08:00.410 --> 08:02.660
getting cold feet, are you?

08:07.780 --> 08:08.370
What?

08:08.370 --> 08:09.100
Pinky promise.

08:18.340 --> 08:20.730
No take-backs.

08:51.730 --> 08:53.850
Our program two days ago

08:53.900 --> 08:55.280
brought increased attention

08:55.280 --> 08:56.050
to the disappearance of Qiao Qingyu,

08:56.050 --> 08:58.340
a high school student in Huanzhou.

08:58.460 --> 09:00.540
Many have provided leads.

09:00.780 --> 09:01.810
Unfortunately,

09:01.810 --> 09:03.370
police and Qingyu's family

09:03.380 --> 09:05.260
[Huanzhou TV]
have verified

09:05.340 --> 09:07.930
that none of the leads are substantive.

09:08.290 --> 09:09.100
It's now been

09:09.100 --> 09:10.020
five days

09:10.020 --> 09:11.660
since Qingyu went missing.

09:11.730 --> 09:13.290
Our 24/7 hot-line

09:13.290 --> 09:14.980
remains open

09:15.220 --> 09:17.050
to receive any information

09:17.050 --> 09:19.220
that may assist in the investigation.

09:49.100 --> 09:50.100
We've got eight or nine hours left

09:50.100 --> 09:51.460
before we leave Huanzhou.

09:52.170 --> 09:54.730
Do you think our adventure

09:55.330 --> 09:56.970
will be like those in the movies?

09:58.890 --> 10:00.490
What adventure?

10:00.700 --> 10:01.940
You've been watching
too many spy movies.

10:01.940 --> 10:02.770
No.

10:03.890 --> 10:05.650
I'm thinking of something

10:06.370 --> 10:07.940
more like Roman Holiday.

10:10.340 --> 10:11.980
Once we leave here,

10:12.420 --> 10:14.130
no one will be able
to control us anymore.

10:14.180 --> 10:15.220
What do you want to do?

10:23.370 --> 10:24.820
I want to eat a hamburger,

10:25.580 --> 10:26.850
go to an amusement park,

10:27.580 --> 10:29.580
and see a lighthouse by the sea.

10:30.250 --> 10:31.060
That's it?

10:36.890 --> 10:38.300
Qiao Qingyu,

10:39.060 --> 10:40.490
is that all you dream of?

10:41.460 --> 10:43.250
Don't mock me

10:43.250 --> 10:45.060
just because you're from the city
and I'm from a small town.

10:45.300 --> 10:46.300
I wouldn't dare.

10:48.700 --> 10:50.650
What about you? What do you want to do?

10:55.220 --> 10:56.010
I want

10:57.100 --> 10:58.130
to get an Afro,

11:00.180 --> 11:01.890
watch a soccer game in a bar,

11:02.850 --> 11:04.060
and go to a concert

11:04.890 --> 11:06.010
and sit in the front row.

11:08.940 --> 11:09.940
Basically,

11:10.420 --> 11:11.700
do all the things adults do.

11:12.060 --> 11:14.370
Everything I've always wanted to do

11:14.370 --> 11:15.250
but couldn't.

11:20.650 --> 11:21.580
Qiao Qingyu.

11:22.180 --> 11:23.820
The moon tonight

11:26.530 --> 11:27.370
is beautiful.

11:33.820 --> 11:34.650
Indeed.

11:37.100 --> 11:37.980
Let's go to sleep.

11:55.060 --> 11:55.940
Qiao Qingyu.

11:58.130 --> 11:59.460
The moon tonight

12:00.850 --> 12:02.010
is truly beautiful.

12:15.100 --> 12:16.850
Can we take Chirpy with us?

12:17.820 --> 12:18.580
Sure.

12:19.820 --> 12:21.130
Let's go, Chirpy.

12:21.700 --> 12:22.490
Wear this outfit

12:22.490 --> 12:23.610
when you leave.

12:23.730 --> 12:25.100
Everyone knows what you wore

12:25.250 --> 12:26.850
when you left,

12:26.940 --> 12:28.180
so putting on this
will help keep you unnoticed.

12:28.940 --> 12:30.220
I'll go down and get us a cab.

12:30.340 --> 12:31.340
Check the house

12:31.340 --> 12:32.530
to make sure you didn't forget anything.

12:32.890 --> 12:33.700
Remember.

12:33.940 --> 12:35.610
Only come down when I call you.

12:40.220 --> 12:41.100
Ming Sheng.

12:43.300 --> 12:44.010
What?

12:46.370 --> 12:47.180
Thank you.

12:47.530 --> 12:49.180
I'll remember what you've done for me.

12:50.420 --> 12:52.300
Why are you being so sentimental?

12:52.850 --> 12:53.700
Wait for me.

13:21.010 --> 13:22.530
Sir, do you go to Jiangzhou?

13:22.940 --> 13:24.220
Too far. No.

14:12.580 --> 14:14.250
Sir, will you take us to Jiangzhou?

14:14.490 --> 14:15.420
Yes. Get in.

14:15.420 --> 14:16.770
Okay. Give me a moment.

14:16.770 --> 14:17.420
There's someone else with me,

14:17.420 --> 14:18.490
and I need to grab our luggage.

14:18.530 --> 14:18.940
All right.

14:31.650 --> 14:33.530
Last night, our local news hot-line

14:33.530 --> 14:35.610
received a tip from a concerned citizen

14:35.650 --> 14:37.490
that Qiao Qingyu was spotted
at a classmate's house

14:37.490 --> 14:38.700
in Chaoyang Village.

14:38.770 --> 14:39.490
This morning,

14:39.490 --> 14:41.220
we rushed to Chaoyang Village.

14:41.220 --> 14:42.180
Are you Qiao Qingyu?

14:42.460 --> 14:43.340
Are you Qiao Qingyu?

14:43.340 --> 14:44.370
She's here!

14:44.370 --> 14:45.370
Qingyu! Qingyu!

14:45.420 --> 14:46.700
Qingyu! Where have you been?

14:47.060 --> 14:48.370
Where have you been, Qingyu?

14:48.850 --> 14:50.010
Are you Qiao Qingyu?

14:50.490 --> 14:51.490
Where have you been?

14:51.490 --> 14:53.300
Let me go!

15:06.130 --> 15:06.460
Where have you been?

15:06.460 --> 15:07.460
Everyone's been worried about you!

15:07.460 --> 15:08.420
Your family has done
everything they could

15:08.420 --> 15:09.770
to find you these past few days.

15:09.770 --> 15:11.100
How could you be so thoughtless?

15:11.100 --> 15:12.460
- So irresponsible!
- That's right!

15:23.850 --> 15:24.580
Where were you?

15:24.580 --> 15:25.650
Your mother was so worried!

15:33.940 --> 15:34.730
Ming Sheng.

15:36.820 --> 15:37.610
What?

15:38.890 --> 15:39.770
Thank you.

15:40.220 --> 15:41.820
I'll remember what you've done for me.

16:02.100 --> 16:03.980
Your mother's been crying
for days at home.

16:04.220 --> 16:04.770
She's worried sick...

16:04.770 --> 16:05.340
Qingyu!

16:05.610 --> 16:06.420
...that something happened to you.

16:06.890 --> 16:08.130
How could you be so irresponsible?

16:20.370 --> 16:21.490
Where have you been?

16:27.060 --> 16:28.220
So you just decided to show up?

16:29.980 --> 16:30.890
Say something!

16:32.490 --> 16:34.100
After all this time?

16:49.220 --> 16:50.220
You almost worried me to death!

16:50.220 --> 16:51.130
Let's talk at home.

16:51.130 --> 16:51.820
Qiao.

16:52.220 --> 16:53.490
Make sure to keep an eye
on your daughter.

16:53.490 --> 16:54.010
Will do.

16:54.010 --> 16:55.220
Mr. Qiao,
you've finally found your daughter.

16:55.220 --> 16:56.130
Thank you.

16:56.130 --> 16:56.980
Give us a comment.

16:58.580 --> 17:00.180
This is a touching moment indeed.

17:00.250 --> 17:01.820
On behalf of the Qiao family,

17:01.850 --> 17:04.420
I'd like to thank
all the kindhearted people

17:04.490 --> 17:05.460
who helped us.

17:05.490 --> 17:06.250
The Qiao family

17:06.250 --> 17:07.770
is finally reunited.

17:12.650 --> 17:14.420
Grandpa, have some tea.

17:15.130 --> 17:15.940
I don't want it.

17:18.010 --> 17:19.609
Get on your knees!

17:20.099 --> 17:20.890
I won't.

17:22.180 --> 17:23.010
Grandpa!

17:35.850 --> 17:36.980
Do you realize what you've done wrong?

17:38.700 --> 17:39.490
Speak up!

17:40.460 --> 17:41.300
I did nothing wrong.

17:43.980 --> 17:46.580
Just apologize and make peace.

17:47.370 --> 17:48.850
Can't you do that?

17:50.100 --> 17:51.610
Jinrui's wedding

17:51.770 --> 17:53.250
was ruined because of you!

17:53.250 --> 17:54.610
Now they're even talking
about getting divorced!

17:54.700 --> 17:56.370
Your grandmother was so upset
that she fell ill.

17:56.770 --> 17:57.850
All you have to do is apologize!

17:59.130 --> 18:01.220
Jinrui was the one
holding this family together,

18:01.340 --> 18:02.460
and you destroyed everything!

18:02.460 --> 18:04.060
I can hold this family together too!

18:04.220 --> 18:05.300
Don't get ahead of yourself.

18:05.420 --> 18:06.180
Causing all this trouble!

18:06.180 --> 18:07.730
Dad's talking. Don't interrupt!

18:08.250 --> 18:11.180
She turned bad because of you.

18:17.610 --> 18:18.180
Grandpa!

18:18.650 --> 18:19.580
Don't

18:19.700 --> 18:20.980
get yourself worked up.

18:21.420 --> 18:23.300
It's on us for not raising her right.

18:23.340 --> 18:25.060
We'll make sure
she gets proper discipline.

18:26.100 --> 18:28.620
All right. Since the girl's home now,

18:28.700 --> 18:29.770
we should go back.

18:30.770 --> 18:32.420
Let's go.

18:32.420 --> 18:33.250
Let me help, Grandpa.

18:33.330 --> 18:34.490
Come on.

18:36.900 --> 18:37.460
You!

18:37.940 --> 18:39.420
Take her back to our hometown soon.

18:40.380 --> 18:41.490
You owe everyone an explanation

18:41.700 --> 18:43.140
for this whole mess!

18:47.810 --> 18:48.900
Help Qingyu up.

18:49.860 --> 18:50.660
We're off.

18:50.980 --> 18:51.810
Come on.

18:57.180 --> 18:58.810
Look at the mess you've caused!

19:24.900 --> 19:26.090
President, we'll go.

19:26.090 --> 19:26.700
Mm.

19:34.180 --> 19:35.330
Someone called the TV station

19:35.330 --> 19:37.490
and leaked Qiao Qingyu's whereabouts.

19:37.940 --> 19:39.380
The only person
who could have done it is you.

19:41.250 --> 19:42.090
The person who called

19:42.090 --> 19:44.140
was just trying to stop a mistake
from happening.

19:44.810 --> 19:46.860
Why do you always ignore
other people's feelings?

19:47.250 --> 19:49.620
Why do you always interfere in my life
as if it's your right?

19:49.730 --> 19:51.380
I have no time for this.

19:51.380 --> 19:52.770
Being parents

19:53.140 --> 19:55.090
doesn't mean you're always right.

19:55.090 --> 19:55.860
Sheng,

19:57.010 --> 19:58.620
there's no such thing as parents

19:58.620 --> 19:59.900
who don't love their children…

19:59.900 --> 20:00.940
That's just an excuse!

20:03.730 --> 20:04.700
Let me tell you this.

20:05.700 --> 20:07.250
I hate your need to control everything.

20:08.140 --> 20:10.090
I no longer want
to have anything to do with you.

20:10.620 --> 20:11.570
When will you finally disappear

20:11.570 --> 20:13.660
from my life for good?

20:22.460 --> 20:24.460
The day you truly grow up.

20:40.700 --> 20:43.250
[In Operation. Operating Room]

21:10.490 --> 21:11.220
Qiao Qingyu.

21:12.620 --> 21:13.380
Don't go anywhere.

21:15.250 --> 21:16.050
I'll be back soon.

21:16.810 --> 21:17.420
Pinky promise.

21:19.530 --> 21:21.900
No take-backs.

21:53.490 --> 21:54.940
She caused this huge mess!

21:54.980 --> 21:56.420
Why can't she just apologize?

21:57.050 --> 21:57.860
The elder one acts out,

21:57.900 --> 21:59.530
and the younger one is so stubborn.

21:59.620 --> 22:01.530
I don't understand
how you raised them.

22:05.090 --> 22:06.010
It's all my fault.

22:07.010 --> 22:08.290
Everything bad is my fault, all right?

22:08.810 --> 22:10.090
The good things are all credited to you,

22:10.220 --> 22:11.380
and the bad ones are all mine.

22:11.490 --> 22:12.730
I gave birth to three children

22:12.980 --> 22:14.460
and worked hard to raise them.

22:14.860 --> 22:16.180
It's my fault
that they didn't turn out well.

22:16.460 --> 22:17.620
I'm the one who taught them wrong.

22:18.140 --> 22:19.140
So it's okay for your whole family

22:19.140 --> 22:20.620
to point fingers
and scold me, right?

22:20.860 --> 22:22.090
Am I not even allowed to say a word?

22:22.090 --> 22:24.050
Well, you raised the children.

22:24.490 --> 22:25.980
What's wrong
with asking her to apologize?

22:26.420 --> 22:28.660
Teenagers make mistakes, sure,

22:28.730 --> 22:30.420
but she's only 18.

22:30.460 --> 22:31.940
But if you fail to restrain her now,

22:31.940 --> 22:33.900
it'll be more difficult
to restrain her in the future.

22:35.530 --> 22:37.860
How are you going to resolve this?

22:40.050 --> 22:41.620
Dad, I'm hungry.

22:41.660 --> 22:43.220
Is that something I get to decide?

22:43.660 --> 22:44.940
Doesn't your family
get the final say in everything?

22:45.980 --> 22:46.620
Dad.

22:46.900 --> 22:48.250
Make me some noodles.

22:49.770 --> 22:51.290
I want tomato noodles.

23:32.050 --> 23:32.980
You've lost weight.

23:36.490 --> 23:37.900
Your father and I had no choice.

23:38.770 --> 23:40.140
Your grandfather was furious.

23:41.940 --> 23:43.010
We had to put on a show.

23:46.620 --> 23:48.380
You really have guts.

23:50.980 --> 23:51.770
How could you just leave

23:51.770 --> 23:52.980
without saying a word?

23:53.220 --> 23:54.700
The whole family was out
looking for you.

23:55.730 --> 23:57.420
We even reported it to the police.

23:57.660 --> 23:59.010
Where have you been these past few days?

24:03.420 --> 24:04.220
At a classmate's house.

24:04.220 --> 24:05.010
Which classmate's house?

24:05.010 --> 24:06.620
The one across the street.

24:10.180 --> 24:11.860
That boy, Ming Sheng, right?

24:12.180 --> 24:13.730
The jacket and those shoes.
They were his,

24:13.730 --> 24:14.460
weren't they?

24:15.180 --> 24:17.290
We're just classmates.

24:17.460 --> 24:19.220
I was having a fever when he found me.

24:19.460 --> 24:21.220
So he let me stay at his place
for a few days

24:21.220 --> 24:22.180
to help me out.

24:22.330 --> 24:23.660
So, he came to you

24:24.420 --> 24:25.810
and let you stay at his house
for a few days.

24:26.730 --> 24:27.460
Is that it?

24:28.180 --> 24:29.660
Why would he do that?

24:30.090 --> 24:31.050
If you didn't contact him,

24:31.050 --> 24:32.290
how did he find you?

24:32.460 --> 24:33.730
There are only two possibilities:

24:35.010 --> 24:37.770
either he's interested in you,

24:37.940 --> 24:38.860
but for the wrong reasons,

24:39.380 --> 24:40.250
or

24:40.380 --> 24:41.620
you threw yourself at him.

24:41.660 --> 24:42.620
Which is it?

24:42.900 --> 24:44.140
Neither.

24:45.490 --> 24:47.770
He just felt sorry for me
and wanted to help.

24:47.770 --> 24:49.140
You're still defending him.

24:49.330 --> 24:50.290
Do you care about him that much?

24:50.290 --> 24:51.250
I don't.

24:51.980 --> 24:52.900
You don't?

24:53.050 --> 24:54.090
Then what are you

24:55.620 --> 24:56.250
worried about?

24:56.250 --> 24:57.420
I'm not worried.

24:58.980 --> 24:59.530
Oh.

24:59.900 --> 25:01.140
You're afraid I'll go look for him

25:01.140 --> 25:02.660
and embarrass you, right?

25:04.010 --> 25:05.420
If you want to scold someone, scold me.

25:05.490 --> 25:07.730
He helped me out of kindness.
Why go after him?

25:07.730 --> 25:09.180
So, you did throw yourself

25:10.420 --> 25:11.460
at him!

25:16.250 --> 25:17.330
What exactly did you do together

25:17.330 --> 25:18.180
these past few days?

25:19.460 --> 25:20.660
Nothing.

25:20.770 --> 25:21.660
Qiao Qingyu,

25:21.940 --> 25:23.420
do you think you can lie to me
about something like this?

25:24.290 --> 25:25.250
Qiao Qingyu.

25:25.770 --> 25:27.290
You're only 18.

25:28.290 --> 25:30.380
I've told you this countless times!

25:30.380 --> 25:32.660
Why is it so hard to remember?

25:33.090 --> 25:34.330
If people find out about this,

25:34.330 --> 25:35.660
what will they think?

25:35.660 --> 25:37.010
Have you thought about that?

25:37.140 --> 25:39.010
How could you not learn
from your sister's mistake?

25:40.290 --> 25:41.490
I won't just stand by

25:41.490 --> 25:42.660
and watch you end up like her!

25:43.090 --> 25:46.090
Listen to me for once.

25:46.730 --> 25:47.660
You're too young,

25:47.660 --> 25:49.250
too naive to understand.

25:49.420 --> 25:50.700
Why can't you trust us?

25:50.700 --> 25:51.940
Do you think we'd hurt you?

25:52.140 --> 25:54.290
Qiao Beiyu is dead because of you all!

25:55.010 --> 25:57.050
You sent her back
to Nanqiao Village, didn't you?

25:57.380 --> 25:58.530
You handed her over to Qiao Jinrui,

25:58.530 --> 25:59.810
didn't you?

25:59.940 --> 26:01.660
You blame us for everything.

26:01.660 --> 26:03.700
You're always those working the hardest
and acting the most righteous.

26:03.730 --> 26:05.530
Can you reflect on yourselves for once?

26:05.620 --> 26:07.330
You always act morally superior
and make us

26:07.330 --> 26:08.330
feel bad about ourselves.

26:08.420 --> 26:09.250
All you do is push me.

26:09.420 --> 26:10.700
One day, if you push me too far,

26:10.700 --> 26:12.380
you'll destroy me too!

26:14.700 --> 26:16.330
I wouldn't dare.

26:17.620 --> 26:18.980
While you're still fine,

26:20.010 --> 26:22.810
just go.

26:23.090 --> 26:24.010
Stay far away from me.

26:24.010 --> 26:25.420
Stay far away from this family!

26:25.570 --> 26:27.250
Even if you die out there, I won't care!

26:27.770 --> 26:28.570
Go!

26:29.460 --> 26:30.420
Fine, I'll go.

26:36.290 --> 26:37.250
Where do you think you're going?

26:37.570 --> 26:38.700
Get back here!

26:38.700 --> 26:39.290
Mom, don't hit Qingyu!

26:39.290 --> 26:40.290
Get back!

26:47.770 --> 26:49.570
I poured my heart and soul
into raising you.

26:49.570 --> 26:50.460
Mom, don't hit Qingyu!

26:50.570 --> 26:51.770
Mom…

26:51.980 --> 26:53.700
You want to leave?

26:53.900 --> 26:56.420
What gives you the right to leave?

27:16.050 --> 27:17.140
Why did you do that?

27:50.420 --> 27:53.450
[In Operation. Operating Room]

27:56.290 --> 27:57.090
Doctor.

27:57.220 --> 27:58.570
Doctor, how is she?

27:58.770 --> 28:00.460
Tan Qianqian's family?

28:00.700 --> 28:01.290
Yes.

28:01.290 --> 28:03.530
There was an unexpected bleeding
during surgery

28:03.530 --> 28:04.730
and we lost the patient.

28:05.250 --> 28:06.490
We are

28:06.620 --> 28:07.490
deeply sorry.

28:12.980 --> 28:14.330
How could this happen?

28:15.090 --> 28:16.700
What should we do now?

29:11.460 --> 29:14.140
I'll just clean around the wound
with some alcohol.

29:14.180 --> 29:15.180
Bear with it.

29:18.530 --> 29:20.330
Bear with it.

29:21.940 --> 29:22.980
Don't move.

29:25.380 --> 29:26.090
Done.

29:28.050 --> 29:30.620
It looks ugly,

29:30.980 --> 29:32.570
but it's just a scratch.

29:32.570 --> 29:33.810
It'll heal in a couple of days.

29:37.700 --> 29:38.530
Qingyu,

29:39.180 --> 29:41.180
it was wrong of Mom to hit you.

29:41.620 --> 29:44.180
But she was angry.

29:44.490 --> 29:46.290
Stop being so stubborn.

29:46.290 --> 29:47.700
It's just a simple "sorry."

29:47.700 --> 29:48.570
How hard can that be?

29:48.570 --> 29:50.250
Why should I apologize
for something I didn't do?

29:52.290 --> 29:55.380
Dad, Mom, Grandpa,
Uncle Haisheng, Uncle Jiangsheng.

29:55.380 --> 29:56.770
Everyone says you were wrong.

29:56.980 --> 29:58.770
Am I wrong
just because they say I'm wrong?

30:00.700 --> 30:02.770
What else could it be?

30:04.250 --> 30:05.050
When we were kids,

30:05.730 --> 30:07.180
they taught us to be honest,

30:07.180 --> 30:08.940
not to bully others, and not to lie.

30:09.530 --> 30:10.730
But when Qiao Beiyu was bullied,

30:10.730 --> 30:11.730
they lied.

30:12.180 --> 30:13.330
When I exposed the truth,

30:13.330 --> 30:14.700
they said I was wrong.

30:15.090 --> 30:16.940
So, what is right and what is wrong?

30:20.460 --> 30:22.730
I don't know about that.

30:23.180 --> 30:24.090
But

30:24.090 --> 30:25.980
Dad and Mom only want
what's best for you.

30:27.660 --> 30:29.050
I haven't told you this,

30:29.490 --> 30:31.220
but Mom nearly got hit by a car

30:31.660 --> 30:33.420
while looking for you.

30:34.810 --> 30:36.530
Why would she risk her life to find you

30:36.900 --> 30:38.700
if she didn't care about you?

30:48.630 --> 30:52.210
[Painkillers]

31:06.090 --> 31:07.010
Take the medicine.

31:08.620 --> 31:09.900
This medicine won't cure me.

31:11.220 --> 31:12.420
You're sick, so take them.

31:19.050 --> 31:19.730
Take the pills.

31:23.050 --> 31:23.860
Fine.

31:23.900 --> 31:25.220
I'm the one who's sick, okay?

32:43.770 --> 32:44.980
Are you okay?

32:45.860 --> 32:47.290
[Sheng]
Do you need my help with anything?

33:56.490 --> 33:59.380
A big door. An iron gate.

34:00.140 --> 34:02.050
Mom's doubled the locks.

34:02.330 --> 34:03.530
From now on,

34:03.700 --> 34:06.250
you're going to live like Chirpy.

34:30.860 --> 34:31.980
I'm Qiao Qingyu's mother.

34:32.770 --> 34:33.810
Stay away from my daughter.

34:35.090 --> 34:36.900
If you don't leave her alone,

34:37.570 --> 34:38.420
I'll do

34:38.620 --> 34:39.730
anything.

35:07.010 --> 35:09.140
I've returned the clothes
to that boy across the street.

35:11.860 --> 35:12.770
I warned him, too.

35:14.940 --> 35:16.290
If he gets involved with you again,

35:17.380 --> 35:18.860
I'll burn their house down.

35:30.010 --> 35:31.610
Give me your transportation card.

35:33.820 --> 35:34.980
Starting this term,

35:35.170 --> 35:36.980
I'll drop you off

35:37.940 --> 35:39.820
and pick you up at school.

35:40.740 --> 35:42.130
You don't need
to carry any money with you.

35:42.300 --> 35:43.260
If you need something,

35:43.260 --> 35:44.610
tell me, and I'll buy it for you.

35:44.740 --> 35:46.650
I'll top up your meal card every month.

35:47.490 --> 35:48.860
Don't worry about anything else.

35:49.570 --> 35:50.690
Just focus on your studies.

35:52.690 --> 35:54.050
And get this into your head.

35:54.570 --> 35:56.260
Don't tell anyone about what happened

35:56.260 --> 35:57.170
between you and that boy.

35:57.690 --> 35:58.820
Not even your best friend.

35:59.490 --> 36:00.530
Do you understand?

36:04.780 --> 36:06.090
If he tries to contact you again,

36:06.340 --> 36:07.740
let me know.

36:09.740 --> 36:10.690
No more hiding anything from me

36:10.690 --> 36:11.820
from now on.

36:14.050 --> 36:15.490
I don't care about what you think.

36:16.300 --> 36:17.380
You're under my control.

36:17.980 --> 36:19.420
Your dad and I just want two things:

36:19.740 --> 36:20.690
your safety

36:20.690 --> 36:22.170
and a university education.

36:24.130 --> 36:26.090
Once you're in university,

36:26.090 --> 36:27.260
I won't interfere anymore.

36:34.300 --> 36:36.170
I'll go feed the bird.

36:36.610 --> 36:38.340
Didn't I just say not to get distracted?

36:40.170 --> 36:41.860
You can't even take care of yourself.

36:42.490 --> 36:43.340
Set it free.

36:44.010 --> 36:44.980
It's injured.

36:44.980 --> 36:46.650
If I release it now, it'll die.

36:46.780 --> 36:48.460
I'll let it go once it recovers.

36:49.900 --> 36:51.340
It won't affect my studies.

37:11.940 --> 37:13.210
What happened to her face?

37:16.860 --> 37:18.010
That's her on TV, isn't it?

37:37.380 --> 37:38.300
She's

37:38.780 --> 37:40.050
a celebrity now.

37:40.820 --> 37:43.090
Don't even bring it up.
My mom followed the news every day.

37:43.210 --> 37:45.050
She was more invested in it
than I am with the dramas.

37:45.260 --> 37:47.130
When she and her mother hugged
at the end,

37:47.130 --> 37:48.860
my mom cried so hard.

37:48.940 --> 37:51.380
Do you know why she ran away from home?

37:51.610 --> 37:53.170
Don't you watch TV?

37:53.780 --> 37:55.260
I don't, which is why I'm asking.

37:55.380 --> 37:56.460
You can't judge a book by its cover.

37:56.460 --> 37:58.420
Who would've thought
Qiao Qingyu would do all that?

37:58.460 --> 37:59.490
Exactly.

37:59.490 --> 38:01.300
You'd never guess it from her.

38:03.610 --> 38:04.900
You've had it rough.

38:07.130 --> 38:08.130
It's self-study right now.

38:08.300 --> 38:09.420
Stop gossiping.

38:22.170 --> 38:23.210
No more chit-chat.

38:24.050 --> 38:24.860
Focus on your studies.

38:29.130 --> 38:29.980
Mr. Sun.

38:30.130 --> 38:30.650
Yes.

38:31.490 --> 38:33.380
I still don't understand this question
even after reading the solution.

38:33.380 --> 38:34.530
Can you explain it to me again?

38:36.380 --> 38:38.260
This question is about calculating

38:38.260 --> 38:39.090
the weight of barium sulfate.

38:39.090 --> 38:40.010
You got that, right?

38:40.490 --> 38:41.860
The key is in the reaction

38:41.860 --> 38:43.490
between barium ions and sulfate ions,

38:43.490 --> 38:45.260
which forms a precipitate
of barium sulfate.

38:45.340 --> 38:46.300
The white precipitate

38:46.300 --> 38:48.460
is insoluble.

38:48.460 --> 38:50.170
By filtering and drying it,

38:50.170 --> 38:51.570
you can weigh it.

38:51.980 --> 38:52.780
Got it.

38:54.650 --> 38:56.530
Qingyu, come with me.

39:00.210 --> 39:00.860
Qingyu.

39:01.210 --> 39:03.050
I saw that recent news report

39:03.050 --> 39:04.090
about you too.

39:05.260 --> 39:06.780
I don't know the details,

39:06.780 --> 39:08.300
but I'm sure you must have your reasons.

39:09.650 --> 39:10.860
When I was your age,

39:11.010 --> 39:12.050
I was rebellious too.

39:12.690 --> 39:13.780
I spent my entire adolescence

39:13.780 --> 39:15.610
clashing with my parents.

39:17.260 --> 39:18.380
And then?

39:19.090 --> 39:19.900
And then?

39:21.050 --> 39:22.940
And then, like every other kid,

39:23.610 --> 39:24.570
I grew up

39:24.820 --> 39:25.940
and they got old.

39:28.530 --> 39:29.530
I'm telling you this

39:29.530 --> 39:30.610
because I want you to know

39:30.820 --> 39:32.820
it's normal to have your own thoughts
at your age.

39:32.940 --> 39:34.010
But you have to find a balance.

39:35.010 --> 39:36.740
If you think

39:36.740 --> 39:37.460
I can help you

39:37.460 --> 39:38.490
with something,

39:38.570 --> 39:39.610
just let me know.

39:39.690 --> 39:40.780
Don't think of me as your teacher.

39:40.900 --> 39:41.820
Think of me as a friend.

39:42.610 --> 39:43.260
I'm also aware

39:43.860 --> 39:45.940
of your situation at school.

39:46.460 --> 39:47.380
The school has set up

39:47.380 --> 39:49.260
an effective anti-bullying system

39:49.380 --> 39:50.050
and provided contact information

39:50.050 --> 39:53.130
for the vice principal
responsible for campus safety.

39:53.570 --> 39:54.420
If you run into any problems,

39:54.420 --> 39:55.940
you must seek help from the school.

39:57.260 --> 39:58.300
If you need psychological support,

39:58.570 --> 40:00.380
please don't hesitate

40:00.380 --> 40:01.460
to reach out to a counselor.

40:02.420 --> 40:03.260
Don't keep everything

40:03.780 --> 40:04.650
bottled up.

41:53.020 --> 41:56.710
♪Perhaps♪

41:57.220 --> 42:02.920
♪The more we care,
the more careful we become♪

42:04.060 --> 42:09.460
♪Counting the distance
that separates us♪

42:10.460 --> 42:16.020
♪A single step,
and we'd be closer still♪

42:21.690 --> 42:25.360
♪In the future♪

42:25.820 --> 42:31.540
♪Time will reveal this secret♪

42:33.040 --> 42:38.110
♪Waiting is a silent promise♪

42:39.360 --> 42:44.520
♪That never expires♪

42:48.120 --> 42:52.590
♪Turns out that what's on my mind♪

42:53.590 --> 42:57.260
♪Is your name♪

42:57.760 --> 43:02.860
♪The only stubbornness in my heart♪

43:03.940 --> 43:07.160
♪At first sight♪

43:07.590 --> 43:10.870
♪The future has been determined♪

43:11.560 --> 43:17.120
♪Dreams began to feel real♪

43:18.220 --> 43:21.760
♪Turns out that what's on your mind♪

43:22.220 --> 43:26.160
♪Is a place♪

43:26.460 --> 43:32.020
♪Where the same story is held dear♪

43:32.690 --> 43:36.060
♪Fortunately, I'm not sensible enough♪

43:36.390 --> 43:39.860
♪Courage wasn't late too♪

43:40.390 --> 43:46.460
♪Only then does time not betray
our acquaintance♪
